
Unit Lenght:
The unit lenght in Houdini is 1 meter
Edit > Preferences > Hip File Options > Unit Length(m)


Ruler:
The SideFX Labs has a Ruler Tool which can be usefull for measuring objects

      Shelf > + > Shelvers > SideFX Labs 
      Shelf > SideFX Labs > Update Toolset:
            - Release:  509 ( or > )
            - Update
       TAB Menu > Ruler     


Camera Look At
Make a camera look at a point of intressetn (null object)
1. Create Camera
2. Create Null object
3. Shelf > Constraints > Look At
4. Select Camera & press Enter
5. Select Null & press Enter
6. Press Enter Again

